The project is a simulation platform.
It is used for practice and research.

Functionality:

Press 'wsadqe' to slightly rotate camera.
Press 'WSADQE' to rotate camera in course level.

Press 'rf' and 'RF' to move camera forward or backward.

Use left mouse click to select particle. Drag the particle to exert force.
When the mouse is released, the external force given by user is disappeared.

Use right mouse click to nail particle.

Display:

Green sphere --> Particle
Blue sphere  --> Nailed particle
Pink sphere  --> Selected particle
Golden line  --> Spring
Red line     --> External force
White line   --> External force given by user
